  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc8 \u0b85\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb2\u0bcd- \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bae\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Problem in identifying the person killed in Kandakadu rehabilitation camp- Delay in investigations",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to the confusion in the identification of the body of the deceased in the Kantakadu rehabilitation camp, it has been reported that investigations into the incidents that took place a few days ago in the rehabilitation camp have not started properly.",
        "Authorities called those believed to be the parents of the deceased to identify the body but could not confirm that the victim was their son, Morning said.",
        "Asked why they could not identify the slain, the officials said that the slain had escaped from the army and had not gone home for many years, so it would have been difficult for them to identify him.",
        "Officials also pointed out that the parents' consent is necessary to conduct the post-mortem examination, which begins once the victim is identified."
      ],
